Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你终于醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.02,0:00:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.79,0:00:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米库里欧……莱拉……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.56,0:00:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你因为高烧昏睡了三天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.53,0:00:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然有三天？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.90,0:00:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是因为史雷你成为了我的容器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.94,0:00:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是有艾莉莎帮忙 还不知道该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉莎……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.71,0:00:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了！艾莉莎呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.26,0:00:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.63,0:00:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉莎！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了……你醒了……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.28,0:00:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你这么有食欲 应该不用担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:00:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.88,0:01:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉莎你一直在照顾我吧？谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.26,0:01:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才应该道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.17,0:01:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你拔出湖之乙女的圣剑时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令那场祭典中的暴动平息下来时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我心里也无比激动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.63,0:01:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时我最想说的话就是「谢谢」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.39,0:01:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.43,0:01:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.83,0:01:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为表示我的感谢之情 我希望你收下这件东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.29,0:01:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.83,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
